      <b data-is-speakable=3D"">How to travel on a budget : Life Kit</b>   =
<b data-is-speakable=3D"">There are ways to travel on a budget without comp=
letely draining your bank account =E2=80=94 but you might have to let go of=
 the over-the-top luxury travel images you see on Instagram. In this episod=
e, we'll help you travel with intention, save ahead and maximize travel too=
ls to get the best deals and savings on the trips you want to take.</b>
</div>
