p><p>WHALIN: The fees are insane. Yeah.</p><p></p><p>EDELMAN: Yeah. It used=
 to be, like, 2008 - RIP 2008 Airbnbs. That was always the cheapest option,=
 right?</p><p></p><p>(LAUGHTER)</p><p></p><p>EDELMAN: Meanwhile, plenty of =
