 save you money elsewhere.</p><p></p><p>WHALIN: So many people rent Airbnbs=
 because, like, I want to buy food and I'm like, hey, man, you know that th=
e Ibis hotel has a microwave and a mini fridge in the room.</p><p></p><p>ED=
ELMAN: And while you may think of hostels as crowded spots filled with coll=
ege-age backpackers, a little creative research will help you find the ones=
