They're really - yeah. They're really amazing and clean and safe. And I'll =
tell you, I've never felt safer as a single mom. And I love a family hostel=
. I've done them in Spain and Germany and Finland and Norway, and I have ne=
ver regretted it.</p><p></p><p>EDELMAN: But there's a fine line between dea=
ls and discomforts. One thing you should never compromise on to save a few =
