 for me, because I wouldn't feel safe.</p><p></p><p>EDELMAN: Brittney also =
takes care, not just with accommodations, but where she decides to travel.<=
/p><p></p><p>OLIVER: That is so important because as a Black woman, there's=
 a lot of places that haven't really seen a lot of Black people. And so we'=
re just rare, unique, when we go in those spaces, and that can cause safety=
