 LGBTQ travelers, disabled travelers and more. And if you'd feel more comfo=
rtable traveling in a group, Brittney recommends doing group travel with co=
mpanies like Travel Noir. Plus planning and communication are free.</p><p><=
/p><p>OLIVER: Just let people know where you are. And then think about - if=
