. If you're a frequent traveler, don't overlook credit card points as the p=
otential to pay your way or at least part of it. Brittney uses her credit c=
ard for large purchases pre-travel, particularly items that earn the most p=
oints, like entertainment and dining out.</p><p></p><p>OLIVER: Before you e=
